message.content: Ewe, ndiyakunceda ngokwenzeka kwamaziko akho. Ndibuye ndikuncede ngokungazinzi kwezoqoqosho nokulawula imali. Ndifuna ukwazi ukuba kunjani ukwenza iindlela eziyiphi zokwenza okanye ukuzama ukuphucula imali. Ndifuna ke ukuba undicaciselele ngemali ephuma kwi-ATM, ukususa imali kwi-intanethi, nokufumana amanani okuncintisana nokufutshaneza. Ndibuye ndikuncede ngokunyanzela okanye ndifake imiyalelo ngokomnqweno wakho. Ndicaciselele kumaziko akho apha.
